{"tid":1476052,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"暫時放棄去英國留學係咪啱既選擇","createTime":"2019-08-15T16:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T18:42:05.000Z","uid":305687,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f55eccb116dec3c0c0e6a41478662516533f67c3","tid":1476052,"uid":305687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:21:08.000Z","msg":"我自己本身有birmingham sport health&amp;exercise sci offer 想讀完繼續讀master 但轉去physio<br />\n可惜屋企人話5年太貴 只可以俾到master既兩年<br />\n所以我最後決定留返係hk讀nursing 但間學校係東華<br />\n其實我而家放棄咗 去讀一個自己興趣相對無pt咁大既科係咪啱既選擇<br />\n雖然有機會exchange 但東華只可以去十幾日 唔似其他u咁一個sem甚至一年<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲打評價下birmingham？見佢pt呢科本來都連續三年uk排第一 點知今年跌到落第四....<br />\n如果真係想讀pt aus定uk會好啲？邊間u又會勁啲？<br />\n<br />\n自己真係好有決心返去pt 希望gpa keep住around3.5"},{"pid":"9972bf503f5060f87288749b10278a1c1a028ea2","tid":1476052,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:24:42.000Z","msg":"我之前個prof. 話BirminghamU=香港嘅shitty嘅評價"},{"pid":"f98a75b79d722d406da956ca6a3de933fbd52649","tid":1476052,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:25:38.000Z","msg":"其實出國讀野雞U不如留返喺香港讀三大啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bcda18b782080dd43ab1a7efeb9c451864f065b","tid":1476052,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:26:53.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行過路過入嚟望下，千載難逢嘅機會啊！８２３和理非<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人鏈</span></span></strong>，萬人齊築香江路！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［和理非升級］一生人一次嘅機會嚟喇！！！！想唔想上Buzzfeed 9GAG？！？！？！？！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475842\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475842</a>"},{"pid":"4c71f843ac7e94af6c5e1fd5b934